FSM-Arrow

FSM::Arrow - an event-driven inheritable generic state machine.

See README.md, this file may be outdated.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc FSM::Arrow

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=FSM-Arrow

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/FSM-Arrow

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/FSM-Arrow

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/FSM-Arrow/


